Package: IPinquiry4
Type: Package
Title: Statistical analysis and data visualisation for co-immunoprecipitation coupled to mass spectrometry experiments
Version: 0.4.5
Author: Helene Zuber and Timothee Vincent
Maintainer: Helene Zuber <helene.zuber@ibmp-cnrs.unistra.fr>
Description: IPinquiry package compiles several functions to: i) identify protein significanlty enriched in co-IP experiment, ii) to retrieve annotation for detected proteins, iii)to vizualize data generating differents type of graphs, such as volcano plot, MDS or heatmap.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 2.15)
Imports: 
    edgeR,
    limma,
    statmod
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    xlsx,
    RColorBrewer,
    pheatmap,
    DT,
    plotly,
    biomaRt,
    htmlwidgets
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
